<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Store - eFootball HUB</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #050a18; --card: #121e36; --primary: #6a11cb; --text: #ffffff; }
        body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; margin: 0; text-align: center; }
        .header { display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .back-btn { color: var(--text); font-size: 24px; text-decoration: none; }
        .store-card { background: var(--card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #1e2d4d; }
        .btn-buy { 
            width: 100%; border: none; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc); color: white; 
            font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <a href="index.html" class="back-btn"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i></a>
        <h2 style="flex:1; margin:0;">GP STORE</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="store-card">
        <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket" style="font-size: 50px; color: #a78bfa; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
        <h3>Welcome to Store</h3>
        <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 14px;">এখানে আপনি আপনার অর্জিত GP দিয়ে স্পেশাল আইটেম কিনতে পারবেন।</p>
        
        <!-- স্টোর বাটন -->
        <button class="btn-buy" onclick="alert('স্টোর আইটেম শীঘ্রই আসছে!')">
            <i class="fas fa-cart-plus"></i> BUY SPECIAL PACK
        </button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
